<st>
Personal life</st>
<p>

Carillo splits her time between <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../132/109132.xml">
Naples, Florida</link></village>
, and New York's <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.8">
<region wordnetid="108630985" confidence="0.8">
<vicinity wordnetid="108641113" confidence="0.8">
<area wordnetid="108497294" confidence="0.8">
<location wordnetid="100027167" confidence="0.8">
<tract wordnetid="108673395" confidence="0.8">
<geographical_area wordnetid="108574314" confidence="0.8">
<district wordnetid="108552138" confidence="0.8">
<section wordnetid="108648322" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../011/13011.xml">
Greenwich Village</link></section>
</district>
</geographical_area>
</tract>
</location>
</area>
</vicinity>
</region>
</site>
. She was married for 15 years to tennis instructor Bill Bowden. They divorced in 1998 and have two children.</p>

